<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="<%= locals.isZh ? 'zh-CN' : 'en' %>">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <%- include('partials/seo-meta', {
        title: '404 页面未找到 - PhotoGongju在线证件照工具',
        description: '您访问的页面不存在。PhotoGongju提供免费在线证件照制作，支持一寸二寸照片、换底色、抠图等功能。',
        keywords: '404,页面未找到,证件照制作,在线证件照',
        noindex: true
    }) %>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <style>
        .error-404-wrap {
            min-height: calc(100vh - 64px - 80px);
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #e2e8f0 100%);
            padding: 40px 20px; text-align: center;
        }
        .error-404-card {
            background: #fff; border-radius: 16px; padding: 60px 40px;
            max-width: 600px; width: 100%; box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .error-code { font-size: 6rem; font-weight: 900; color: #6366f1; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        .error-title { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px; color: #1e293b; }
        .error-desc { color: #64748b; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 32px; }
        .error-links { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px; justify-content: center; }
        .error-link-card {
            display: block; padding: 12px 20px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 10px; color: #334155; text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.9rem; transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .error-link-card:hover {
            border-color: #6366f1; background: #eef2ff; text-decoration: none;
            transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(99,102,241,0.12);
        }
        .error-link-card .icon { font-size: 1.2rem; margin-right: 4px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<nav class="navbar">
    <div class="container">
        <a href="/" class="navbar-brand">
            <span class="brand-icon">🖼️</span>
            <span class="brand-text">PhotoGongju</span>
        </a>
    </div>
</nav>

<div class="error-404-wrap">
    <div class="error-404-card">
        <div class="error-code">404</div>
        <h1 class="error-title">页面未找到</h1>
        <p class="error-desc">
            您访问的页面可能已被删除、更名或暂时不可用。<br>
            请尝试以下热门工具页面：
        </p>
        <div class="error-links">
            <a href="/" class="error-link-card"><span class="icon">🏠</span> 返回首页</a>
            <a href="/upload" class="error-link-card"><span class="icon">📷</span> 证件照制作</a>
            <a href="/tutorial" class="error-link-card"><span class="icon">📖</span> 教程中心</a>
            <a href="/tutorial/how-to-take-id-photo" class="error-link-card"><span class="icon">🎓</span> 证件照拍摄教程</a>
            <a href="/tutorial/change-background" class="error-link-card"><span class="icon">🎨</span> 换底色教程</a>
            <a href="/tutorial/visa-photo-guide" class="error-link-card"><span class="icon">✈️</span> 签证照片指南</a>
            <a href="/size-library" class="error-link-card"><span class="icon">📐</span> 尺寸规格大全</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<footer class="footer">
    <div class="container"><p>&copy; 2024 PhotoGongju — 在线证件照制作工具</p></div>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
